snippet.title: I Ate At 7-Elevens Across Asia
snippet.description:
Thanks again to Rosetta Stone for sponsoring this video!! Start your language journey today at¬†https://partners.rosettastone.com/safiyanygaard for an exclusive discount of over 60% off an unlimited lifetime language subscription!! üç°

#rosettastone #rosettastonepartner 

EDIT: Also, there is some controversy around birds nest products that we weren't aware of before filming, our apologies. If you'd like to know more, here are a couple of links to some more information -

https://www.businessinsider.com/birds-nest-delicacy-asia-price-farming-benefits-2021-3
https://tableagent.com/article/birds-nest-soup-savory-delicacy-or-gourmet-cruelty/
https://naturalnest.com/blogs/news/ethics-of-harvesting-bird-nests-the-what-you-need-to-know?srsltid=AfmBOorW9H0KXEyJVxYXWB6E-6dxs2C64u3zRrl0MTJ3y9cYnDNyG5M4

HELLO FRIENDS!! And welcome to the 7-Eleven haul of my dreams!! Now, on our previous trips to East Asia, we definitely noticed the prevalence of 7-Elevens pretty much everywhere - and not only were we surprised by how widespread and popular they were - we quickly realized, they had a lot of pretty awesome stuff we don‚Äôt have in the states - like, baos, teas, sandos, noodles, iced coffees, unique chip flavors, pancake sandwiches, corn ice cream - and more!! And once we returned - I started to notice how many people online were also going to international 7-Elevens and doing snack hauls - and I realized - this is a convenience store movement!! 

So on our travels over the past year, we‚Äôve collected 7-Eleven tours and hauls in each country we visited - Singapore, Malaysia, and Japan‚Ä¶ to try out some viral snacks, and generally compare them, but also mostly just to feast! Which country‚Äôs 7-Eleven should we visit next?

https://www.businessinsider.com/birds-nest-delicacy-asia-price-farming-benefits-2021-3

CIAO AMICI!! E benvenuti al bottino da 7-Eleven dei miei sogni!! Ora, nei nostri precedenti viaggi in Asia orientale, abbiamo sicuramente notato la presenza di 7-Eleven praticamente ovunque, e non solo siamo rimasti sorpresi dalla loro diffusione e popolarit√†, ma ci siamo subito resi conto che avevano un sacco di cose fantastiche che non abbiamo negli Stati Uniti, come bao, t√®, sando, noodles, caff√® freddo, patatine dai gusti unici, panini con pancake, gelato al mais e molto altro! E una volta tornati, ho iniziato a notare quante persone online andavano anche nei 7-Eleven internazionali e facevano haul di snack, e ho capito: questo √® un movimento di minimarket!

Cos√¨, nei nostri viaggi dell'ultimo anno, abbiamo raccolto tour e haul di 7-Eleven in ogni paese che abbiamo visitato: Singapore, Malesia e Giappone... per provare alcuni snack virali e, in generale, confrontarli, ma anche e soprattutto per fare un piccolo assaggio! Quale 7-Eleven di un paese dovremmo visitare la prossima volta?

en.description:
Thanks again to Rosetta Stone for sponsoring this video!! Start your language journey today at¬†https://partners.rosettastone.com/safiyanygaard for an exclusive discount of over 60% off an unlimited lifetime language subscription!! üç°

EDIT: Also, there is some controversy around birds nest products that we weren't aware of before filming, our apologies. If you'd like to know more, here are a couple of links to some more information -

https://www.businessinsider.com/birds-nest-delicacy-asia-price-farming-benefits-2021-3
https://tableagent.com/article/birds-nest-soup-savory-delicacy-or-gourmet-cruelty/

HELLO FRIENDS!! And welcome to the 7-Eleven haul of my dreams!! Now, on our previous trips to East Asia, we definitely noticed the prevalence of 7-Elevens pretty much everywhere - and not only were we surprised by how widespread and popular they were - we quickly realized, they had a lot of pretty awesome stuff we don‚Äôt have in the states - like, baos, teas, sandos, noodles, iced coffees, unique chip flavors, pancake sandwiches, corn ice cream - and more!! And once we returned - I started to notice how many people online were also going to international 7-Elevens and doing snack hauls - and I realized - this is a convenience store movement!! 

So on our travels over the past year, we‚Äôve collected 7-Eleven tours and hauls in each country we visited - Singapore, Malaysia, and Japan‚Ä¶ to try out some viral snacks, and generally compare them, but also mostly just to feast! Which country‚Äôs 7-Eleven should we visit next?

snippet.title: Mid-East Crisis escalates - Iran rains missiles on Israel after attacks on nuclear sites | BBC News
snippet.description:
Iran has launched mass new strikes on Israel.  It says it attacked dozens of targets including military centres and airbases. ¬† Smoke has been seen rising over the skyscrapers of Tel Aviv and there have been explosions in Jerusalem. ¬†

The  bombardment is in retaliation for Israel's strikes on Iran, hitting military and nuclear sites.   It says it hit a nuclear facility in Isfahan following earlier strikes on the country's biggest nuclear facility at Natanz .Israel said the attacks were vital to prevent Iran developing a nuclear weapon. ¬†

Iran‚Äôs spiritual leader, Ayatollah Khamenei, promised his country would 'inflict heavy blows' in response.
¬†
There are warnings the conflict could escalate into all-out war.  

Jane Hill presents BBC News at Ten reporting by Lucy Williamson, Ione Wells, Frank Gardner, Tom Bateman, Gary O‚ÄôDonoghue and Lyse Doucet.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS - Soccer Aid 2025 | England v World XI | Tomlinson, Zuu, Tevez, Ginge, Rooney & More!
snippet.description:
DONATE HERE: https://www.itv.com/socceraid

Soccer Aid for UNICEF returns to Old Trafford, Manchester this June. Uniting celebrities and footballing legends to battle it out on the pitch as England take on the Soccer Aid World XI FC in the world‚Äôs biggest charity football match.

England took the crown last summer meaning this year there‚Äôs everything to play for ‚Äì and with an incredible lineup of stars, this is shaping up to be a thrilling match. Fan favourites Jill Scott, Tom Grennan and Sir Mo Farah are joined by exciting new signings Tyson Fury, Joe Hart, Steph Houghton, Leonardo Bonucci and many more! This year also sees the hotly anticipated return of Soccer Aid stars including Louis Tomlinson and Wayne Rooney ‚Äì one of the greatest footballers of all time ‚Äì who will be on former home ground at Old Trafford, Manchester.

snippet.title: First Class on the World's Newest Airline (Global Airlines)
snippet.description:
Get $50 off Daily Drop Pro! -¬†https://s.dailydrop.com/yt_kn-summer25
Our FREE Miles & Points 101 Course - https://s.dailydrop.com/kn_101
Our FREE Daily Drop Newsletter -¬†https://s.dailydrop.com/kn_sign-up

Join us on our first inaugural flight experience!! We flew on Global Airlines first ever flight from Manchester Airport to JFK, New York in first class! This airline was started buy a guy who we've followed on instagram for years and had never met...until today ;)

Huge thanks to James and the Global Airlines team for having us on this unforgettable flight! (and for giving us 50% off our tickets!)

Episode 962 | Filmed May 2025

Subscribe to our new friend ¬†@jameswarrenolivertravelexpert¬† :)
 https://youtu.be/W92wnw7Ytq8?si=yj_Jm5asGT03YMJo 

‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî

Who are Kara and Nate?! 

2016-2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FuFv4iF8wgg&t=1s 

2020-2024: https://youtu.be/ikAN9e0gBaU?si=G644UGWIqPrOzTYW

Originally from Nashville, Tennessee, we got married 2013 and were super ‚Äúnormal.‚Äù I was a teacher and Nate started a small printing business from the spare bedroom of our apartment. 

We discovered the world of ‚Äútravel hacking‚Äù while planning our honeymoon & became addicted ;)

So after 2 years of obsessively saving $35k and over 2 million miles and points, we sold our cars and apartment and left home January 10, 2016 for a ‚Äúone year‚Äù trip around the world.

Our goal was to see as many places as possible before we ran out of money and went back home to ‚Äúnormal life.‚Äù We started this channel to share our experiences with friends and family, but quickly fell in love with living on the road and found a new passion for capturing our travels through video. So we did everything we could to keep going.

4 years later, we achieved our new goal of visiting 100 countries and all 7 continents. We had no plans to slow down, until 2020 forced us to ;) Which is when we bought a converted van to start exploring our own country for the first time!

After ~2 years of van life, we are back to full time international traveling! And now we are in our 10TH YEAR of finding the best adventures the world has to offer :) 

We are incredibly grateful to be able to continue doing something we love every day. üòäüé•üåé Thank you to everyone who has been a part of our journey!

snippet.title: Epic Fire Experiments w/ Unspeakable!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the second week of Camp CrunchLabs! This week Unspeakable joins us for some epic fire experiments! It's not too late to join Camp CrunchLabs! Join here: http://www.campcrunchlabs.com 

Check out Disney's Elio, only in theaters June 20: https://movies.disney.com/elio
#Elio

Each build-it-yourself STEM toy teaches the magic and fun in engineering principles and coincides with exclusive weekly videos like this one that accelerate your learning! Ready for Camp? Visit http://www.campcrunchlabs.com for more info.

A big thanks to our special guest @Unspeakable  for joining me on Venus!

Week 1 Super Challenge Montage: https://youtu.be/O-zch46IFSY?si=N-ypEfL2RpXTcExw

This weeks Challenge:
HACK YOUR FOOD LIKE AN ENGINEER!
This 10-Day challenge requires you to embrace the wonderful world of food. Solve a food problem - like food that's too crummy or spills too easily or that needs a clever protection. Maybe you can come up with a smart way to make a CrunchLab logo out of food, or build a device that makes cooking easier, or maybe engineer something to feed yourself.

As always, be safe and get a parent's permission before building. Once you've filmed it, work with your parents to share it with us!"

HOW TO SUBMIT YOUR CHALLENGES?
Parents: Tag challenge project video submissions @crunchlabs with #CampCrunchlabsContest on Instagram, X, TikTok or Facebook. Then complete this form https://www.crunchlabs.com/pages/camp-planet-page-venus

NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Contest begins at 9:00 a.m. PT on 6/7/25 & ends 11:59 p.m. PT on 7/23/25; but, to be eligible to win Grand Prize, one must enter by 11:59 p.m. PT on 7/8/25. Open to legal residents of the 50 U.S. & D.C., who are 18+ and the parent or legal guardian of at least (1) child between 8-16 years of age. Grand Prize winner must travel 7/20/25-7/22/25. See Official Rules for full details including entry periods, entry requirements, prize descriptions and judging criteria. Void where prohibited.
Full rules: http://crunchlabs.com/camp-rules

snippet.description:
Colors + Candy Theme = Perfection?! Come with me and indulge in this sugary sweet series of dolls with the first of six to come: Red!
--------------------------------------------
Merchandise https://www.dollightful.shop/
Doll clothing patterns for sale: https://www.etsy.com/shop/DollightfulPatterns
Instagram, Twitter, Pinterest: @dollightfully
--------------------------------------------
MATERIALS:
Monster High Doll ‚ÄúDraculaura‚Äù (Generation 3)
Nylon doll hair from https://dollyhair.com/
Doll hair tools from https://www.etsy.com/shop/TheDollPlanetHair
Rooting tool and needles (drill chuck + needle with its eye cut at an angle)
Mr.Super Clear UV Flat (wear a mask and spray in a ventilated area!)
Mask - Organic Vapor Particle Respirator Mask 
Gouache paint
Water colored Pencils -Faber Castell
High Gloss Varnish ‚Äì Liquitex
Air Dry Clay -Premier
Acrylic paint ‚Äì Liquitex, Alpha
Literal trash I found on the ground (Mylar ballon, vinyl packaging)
--------------------------------------------
SPOONFLOWER (fabric printing service) info‚Ä¶.
For cotton, I chose their ‚ÄúPetal Signature Cotton‚Äù option on the ‚Äú1 yard (42‚Äùx36‚Äù)‚Äù. My file size was 6300x5400px, 150 dpi.
For stretchy knit, I chose their ‚ÄúJersey1‚Äù option on the ‚Äúfat quarter (28‚Äùx18‚Äù)‚Äù. My file size was 4200x2700px, 150 dpi.
For satin, I chose their ‚ÄúSatin1‚Äù option on the ‚Äúfat quarter (27‚Äùx18‚Äù)‚Äù. My file size was 4050x2700px, 150 dpi.
--------------------------------------------
Dollightful theme song ‚ÄúBubble Pop‚Äù was made in Garage Band using royalty-free loops.
Other musical tracks & SFX from Artlist https://artlist.io 
Ariel Shalom ‚Äì Raindrops (Instrumental Version)
Jimit ‚Äì Looku Looku (Instrumental Version)
Saggie ‚Äì Easty to Love (Instrumental Version)
Aves ‚Äì God is a Girl (Instrumental Version)
LOLEK ‚Äì Cruise Control
Rex Banner ‚Äì Weekend (Instrumental Version)
Lemon ‚Äì Plastic Generation (Instrumental Version)
--------------------------------------------
Logo and some graphics designed by: https://charliesparksdesign.myportfolio.com/
Some graphics designed by me.
--------------------------------------------

snippet.title: YOU Ranked My Characters. I'm SHOCKED.
snippet.description:
___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Friday at 4:00pm ET

___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh) Elizabeth and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 30 and like doing creative activities (mostly painting on things), or really anything that gives me an excuse to use rainbows, sprinkles and my own cutesy characters in excess. I'm heavy into editing, so my video are chok-full of sound effects, filters and lil....moments, or as we like to call them "MEmes." I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and various other items I find. I also love to draw, traditionally and digitally. I'm not the most skilled artist out here, but I like to focus on having fun with creativity and being able to laugh at my own mistakes. 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Drawings to Squishies: turning my flat drawings into squishies
Finishing Art Ideas: Choosing art ideas from my giant list and making them happen
Squishies I've Been Avoiding: Painting on the squishies I DON'T want to paint

LYRICS
I check the doors, check the windows, and pull the blinds,
I check the clock, wondering what he‚Äôll pull this time,
I have a feeling that necromancer‚Äôs outside,
And I‚Äôm just trying to stay quiet.

I don‚Äôt sleep much, that's crazy, how‚Äôd you know that?
Keep myself up, that's maybe how you know that,
Promises and contracts I used to keep,
I don‚Äôt sleep much, that's crazy, how‚Äôd you know that?
Keep myself up, that‚Äôs maybe how you know that,
My hallucination I used to see.

Wake up and I find out, did a change up,
Wait ‚Äî Did it change up?
Is it light out yet?
Better find out. Bet,
Imma walk around the edge of the room,
And the bed where I hide my face,
Pace around,
Better try to breathe,
Pace around, Pace around.

(Sleep I found)
I wanna get out there,
But I don‚Äôt try,
I wanna get out there,
But I don‚Äôt try.

I used to see,
It felt so real,
But now I plead,
Just take the deal,
I promised you,
A contract.

snippet.title: The Sims 4 Enchanted by Nature | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sims‚Ñ¢ 4 Enchanted by Nature Expansion Pack* arrives July 10 and is available for pre-order now: http://ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack


Order now through Aug 21 for the Fairy Garden Digital Content**: the Lofty Leaf Pond, Luminous Mycena Lantern, and Disguised Dwelling Fairy Home.

Indulge your sense of wonder: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/news/enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack
Live surrounded by nature and embrace a free spirited lifestyle. Who needs beds and plumbing? It's time to get comfy in the great outdoors by meeting your Sims' needs in nature and Foraging for food and collectables. 

There's a charming world to explore, and it has a mystical side. Experience strange Ailments, craft Elixirs, and even become a Fairy! When creating Fairy Sims, you'll choose from a variety of beautiful wings which you can paint freely.

Available July 10 at 10AM PT on EA App PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation¬Æ4, and PlayStation¬Æ5. Pre-order now: http://ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack 

*Requires The Sims 4 & all game updates. For PC, see minimum system requirements for the pack.

**CONDITIONS AND RESTRICTIONS APPLY. http://ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-enchanted-by-nature-expansion-pack

snippet.title: Superman | Tickets on Sale Now
snippet.description:
On July 11, the entire world will look up. Get tickets now for #Superman - Only In Theaters and @IMAX 

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (‚ÄúThe Last of Us‚Äù) and editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, ‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

The official YouTube channel of Atlantic Records artist Kehlani.

It doesn‚Äôt really need an explanation‚Äîyou know exactly what Kehlani means when she sings. Without sugarcoating or softening a word, the Bay Area-born two-time GRAMMY¬Æ Award-nominated multiplatinum songstress will drop a hard truth in one breath and flip a middle finger in the next. She may extend a seductive invitation or an empathetic plea before leaving you in your thoughts and feelings. Either way, she finds a way to consistently relate without filter. With each move, she strengthens this connection to listeners everywhere.  Kehlani‚Äôs 2015 breakout mixtape You Should Be Here received a 2016 GRAMMY¬Æ Award nod in the category of ‚ÄúBest Urban Contemporary Album.‚Äù On its heels, her 2017 full-length debut SweetSexySavage bowed at #3 on the Billboard Top 200 and eventually went gold. Between selling out dates on the SweetSexySavage Tour, the record closed out the year on Pitchfork‚Äôs ‚ÄúThe 50 Best Albums of 2017‚Äù and Rolling Stone‚Äôs ‚Äú20 Best R&B Albums of 2017.‚Äù 

Along the way, she contributed to Suicide Squad: The Album and The Fate of the Furious: The Album and guested on Cardi B‚Äôs double-platinum ‚ÄúRing,‚Äù Kyle‚Äôs platinum ‚ÄúPLAYINWITME,‚Äù and Justin Bieber‚Äôs ‚ÄúGet Me,‚Äù to name a few. By 2020, she picked up three gold solo singles‚Äî"You Should Be Here,‚Äù ‚ÄúHoney,‚Äù and ‚ÄúDistraction,‚Äù for which she received her second GRAMMY¬Æ nomination for Best R&B performance. In addition, four platinum singles‚Äî‚ÄúGangsta,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Way‚Äù [feat. Chance the Rapper], ‚ÄúCRZY,‚Äù and ‚ÄúNights Like This‚Äù [feat. Ty Dolla $ign] and streams in the billions. Not to mention, Billboard Women In Music honored her with the ‚ÄúRule Breaker Award‚Äù as she gathered nominations at the Soul Train Awards and the American Music Awards. Plus, she made show-stopping appearances at Voodoo Music + More, Coachella, and beyond. In the aftermath of 2019‚Äôs chart-topping While We Wait mixtape, everything changed. She became a mom. As such, parenthood left an indelible imprint on her second full-length, It Was Good Until It Wasn‚Äôt. Out May 8th, It Was Good Until It Wasn‚Äôt is described by Kehlani as her most mature body of work, featuring songs based on her own real experiences including recently released ‚ÄúToxic‚Äù and ‚ÄúEverybody Business.‚Äù In the end, you‚Äôll know exactly what‚Äôs on Kehlani‚Äôs mind, heart, and soul on It Was Good Until It Wasn‚Äôt.

snippet.title: I Tried the Top 50 Airbnbs in America - Day 2
snippet.description:
hello new mexico!!!
donate here - https://www.stjude.org/50states



Wheel of Doom penalties:
1. Running on fumes - You must drive until the tank says ‚Äúempty.‚Äù
2. Local Legend - You must share a meal with a local from the nearest town before moving on.
3. Route Roulette - You must receive directions from a stranger and follow them word for word.
4. Reverse Card - You must turn around the way you came and find another way to your next Airbnb.
5. Detour - You are not allowed to drive on highways to the next Airbnb.
6. Silent Treatment ‚Äì No talking between Ryan & Haley for the entire road trip.
7. Airplane Mode - You must get to your next Airbnb without your phones.
8. Locked Out - You are not allowed to sleep in your next Airbnb.
9. The Split - One of you must split up and find another way to your next Airbnb.
10. Red Light, Green Light - Roll a dice ‚Äî whatever it lands on, you must wait that many hours before hitting the road.
11. Golden Ticket - Congratulations! You have unlocked immunity for 24 hours. It can be activated at any time.

snippet.title: I Built a Giant LEGO Railway for my Pets!
snippet.description:
#ad To celebrate World Play Day 2025, I partnered with The  @LEGO Group to create the ultimate LEGO railway adventure #LEGOWorldPlayDay #LEGOPartner

I Built a Giant LEGO Railway for my Pets! My LEGO train travels through HUGE mountains, glow-in-the-dark and LED lit tunnels and down an insane DIY pool-noodle spiral coaster. But will the train make it or will this end in a complete disaster? 

‚ô° Get the merch: https://aquariuminfo.com/ (worldwide shipping üåé)

SUBSCRIBE for a chance at the ecosystem kit
‚ñ∫  https://www.youtube.com/c/AquariumInfo?sub_confirmation=1

Meet The Crew!
üêà Nori
üê≤ Gizmo
ü¶Ä Noodle & Pickle
ü¶û Mochi
üê¢ Harry 
ü¶ê Ralph
üê∏ Frito & Burrito
ü¶é Lucy & Lemon
üê† Peanut & Jelly
ü¶é Lime & Pepper & Squeak
ü™¶ R.I.P. Kirby

Watch as we build an insane 200ft LEGO railway through the studio, passing by some of your favorite animals, including Ralph my Peacock Mantis Shrimp, Mochi, my grocery store lobster, and the beloved duo Lucy and Lemon, my axolotls. We even build my kitten Nori a rube goldberg contraption to feed him treats when the train passes by! In this adventure-filled episode, we also travel to an abandoned railway to learn about trains in the real world! 

This LEGO train trip will have 5 epic stops, including a dual greenhouse filled with live plants and LEGO botanicals, a snowy mountain featuring miniature Christmas trees and LEGO Santa, a cat cafe, a glow-in-the-dark tunnel with glowing crystals and an arid desert ecosystem with LEGO animals and real cacti. The LEGO train will be equipped with a tiny camera so you can see what the train sees, so be on the lookout for all of the hidden LEGO builds along the way! Can you spot them all?

Watch until the end to see if the train makes it through the entire trip in one piece! This video is perfect for anyone who loves LEGO trains, building custom LEGO builds, axolotls, exotic pets, rare animals, DIY projects or is just interested in what it takes to build an epic DIY LEGO railway! 

If you have any comments, suggestions or questions for this LEGO train video or future videos, leave them down in the comments! Also for additional content like this, video tutorials, project sneak peeks and more, follow me on Instagram @aquariuminfo.

snippet.title: Wiz Khalifa: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
This Black Music Month, Tiny Desk honors the anniversaries of landmark albums that have shaped the course of music and culture.

Bobby Carter | June 10, 2025
Wiz Khalifa‚Äôs Kush & Orange Juice came out 15 years ago. To honor the anniversary, the Pittsburgh emcee assembled a group of Tiny Desk veterans, Pennsylvania natives and his DJ to reimagine highlights from the classic mixtape, plus tracks from Kush & Orange Juice 2, its similar, yet more mature follow-up.

Something was happening during the entire show and lots of us in the room could feel it. We were waiting for him to engage with us, but he didn‚Äôt. I stepped in after a few songs to remind him that it was OK to do so ‚Äî still, nothing. But then, after ‚ÄúCrime Bud and Women,‚Äù Wiz spoke to the audience for the first and only time, wiping away tears: ‚ÄúYou made me cry. F*** y‚Äôall!‚Äù 

I can muster up a few guesses as to why the emotion overflowed. Wiz had a host of family and friends present in this very intimate setting, including his father. And he did tell me how much he loves performing. But honestly, this sonic masterpiece was good enough to hit the tear ducts. 

SET LIST
‚ÄúRed Eye‚Äù 
‚ÄúMezmorized‚Äù 
‚ÄúThe Kid Frankie‚Äù 
‚ÄúNever Been‚Äù
‚ÄúUp‚Äù
‚ÄúCrime Bud and Women‚Äù 

MUSICIANS
Wiz Khalifa: vocals
Kenneth Wright: music director, bass
DJ Bonics: turntables
Uncle Bubz: keys
Russell Gelman-Sheehan: guitar
Kendall Lewis: drums

TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Bobby Carter
Director/Editor: Joshua Bryant
Audio Technical Director: Josh Newell
Video Editor: Kara Frame
Videographers: Joshua Bryant, Kara Frame, Maia Stern
Audio Engineer: Josephine Nyounai
Production Assistants: Ashley Pointer, Dora Levite
Photographer: Catie Dull
Tiny Desk Series Editor: Lars Gotrich
Executive Producer: Suraya Mohamed
Series Creators: Bob Boilen, Stephen Thompson
VP, Visuals and Music: Keith Jenkins

#tinydesk #nprmusic #wizkhalifa

What do we do now?, But Running out of fuel, food & water in the Simpson Desert! Do we make it? 10 days, 1000km in low range, But FLOODED & BOGGED! Do we get out? Once in a decade storm Floods Australia‚Äôs DRIEST town!, But FLOODED Kimberley river crossing GONE WRONG ‚Äì 150m+ wide rapids - our most epic trip EVER FILMED!, But 5 4WDs FLOODED IN CAPE YORK - 1 gets towed home! Frenchmans - the WETTEST we've ever seen it!, But Lake Eyre‚Äôs biggest flood in nearly 50 years | 7.30, But CARAVANS ABANDONED & stuck for 1 week in flooded Australian Outback! Do we get out?, But THE WETTEST WE'VE SEEN CAPE YORK... RAGING rivers & bottomless mud - 1st 4WDs down Tele Track 2023 or any other video like 4WD 24/7, The Grand Tour, Matts Off Road Recovery, Donut Media or Mighty Car Mods would make. This is a video where Jock & Jesse sit down for a ‚Äòtell all‚Äô chat about escaping a once-in-a-lifetime desert flood!

snippet.title: Los Angeles protests against ICE immigration raids continue; U.S. Marines, National Guard deployed
snippet.description:
More National Guard troops and hundreds of Marines have been deployed to Los Angeles as violent protests continued for another night, with more than 100 arrests Monday.

California Gov. Gavin Newsom continued to denounce sending the military into the city, filing an emergency motion to block the Marines' deployment. The National Guard has been protecting a federal complex in LA where some immigrants are being held after ICE raids around the city.

Some of the major announcements include: new ‚ÄúLiquid Glass‚Äù design coming to all systems, new windowing capabilities to iPadOS 26, Messages will get custom backgrounds and new group chat features like Polls. snippet.title: LAPD chief speaks out about deployment of military forces to anti-ICE protests
snippet.description:
